513
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,559
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, uložili su milijarde u integraciju.

514
00:32:37,559 --> 00:32:38,539
[SPEAKER_02] Čak su imali

515
00:32:38,539 --> 00:32:41,000
