516
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,819
[SPEAKER_02] i tako dalje.

517
00:32:41,819 --> 00:32:43,359
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim,

518
00:32:43,359 --> 00:32:45,700
[SPEAKER_02] nisu te politike uspjele.

519
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

520
00:32:46,559 --> 00:32:49,019
[SPEAKER_02] sad bi vam mogao nabrajati

521
00:32:49,019 --> 00:32:49,740
[SPEAKER_02] čitav niz,

522
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:51,799
[SPEAKER_02] ali to je manje više poznato,

523
00:32:51,799 --> 00:32:54,599
[SPEAKER_02] ali tu nastupa imigracijska ideologija,

524
00:32:54,599 --> 00:32:56,440
[SPEAKER_02] koja je cijelo vrijeme tvrdila,

525
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,279
[SPEAKER_02] znači, da to nije točno,

526
00:32:58,279 --> 00:33:00,940
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, da useljenici

527
00:33:00,940 --> 00:33:03,119
[SPEAKER_02] ne guše cijenu rada,

528
00:33:03,119 --> 00:33:04,680
[SPEAKER_02] a studije pokazale da da.

529
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:07,519
[SPEAKER_02] Da ne podižu cijenu nekretnina.

530
00:33:07,519 --> 00:33:09,339
[SPEAKER_02] Studije opet pokazuju da da.

531
00:33:09,339 --> 00:33:11,220
[SPEAKER_02] ili je logično, veća je potražnja.

532
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:13,400
[SPEAKER_02] I opet je mladom Hrvatu teže,

533
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,000
[SPEAKER_02] zato što useljavate

534
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:17,200
[SPEAKER_02] jako puno, stvarate

535
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,319
[SPEAKER_02] potražnju.

536
00:33:19,319 --> 00:33:21,759
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, i useljavanje

537
00:33:21,759 --> 00:33:23,200
[SPEAKER_02] diže cijenu nekretnina.

538
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,400
[SPEAKER_02] Zatim da

539
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,240
[SPEAKER_02] kriminalitet,

540
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:28,900
[SPEAKER_02] znači, velike su polemike bile,

541
00:33:28,900 --> 00:33:30,279
[SPEAKER_02] skrivalo se, znači,

542
00:33:30,279 --> 00:33:31,380
[SPEAKER_02] je u porastu.

543
00:33:31,380 --> 00:33:32,619
[SPEAKER_02] I to ozbiljno.

544
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:34,819
[SPEAKER_02] Pa dobro, to vidimo u Švedskoj, isto tako.

545
00:33:34,819 --> 00:33:36,640
[SPEAKER_02] Gledajte, Njemačka je to skrivala,

546
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:39,059
[SPEAKER_02] znači, 18 puta već u stopu,

547
00:33:39,059 --> 00:33:40,799
[SPEAKER_02] recimo, imate kriminaliteta

548
00:33:40,799 --> 00:33:42,299
[SPEAKER_02] kod nekih

549
00:33:42,299 --> 00:33:44,079
[SPEAKER_02] useljeničkih skupina,

550
00:33:44,079 --> 00:33:46,240
[SPEAKER_02] konkretno Afganistan, Pakistan,

551
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,039
[SPEAKER_02] tako dalje,

552
00:33:47,039 --> 00:33:49,559
[SPEAKER_02] nego kod domicilnog stanovništva.

553
00:33:49,559 --> 00:33:51,359
[SPEAKER_02] Seksualnih napada.

554
00:33:51,359 --> 00:33:54,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, sad se to malo

555
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,779
[SPEAKER_02] ola bavilo

556
00:33:55,779 --> 00:33:57,480
[SPEAKER_02] i čak se smije razgovarati.

557
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,319
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ja uvijek kažem,

558
00:33:58,319 --> 00:34:00,460
[SPEAKER_02] vi već kad smijete o tom razgovarati,

559
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,299
[SPEAKER_02] proces je već...

560
00:34:01,299 --> 00:34:01,619
[SPEAKER_02] Prošlo je.

561
00:34:01,619 --> 00:34:02,980
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

562
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:05,440
[SPEAKER_02] gotovo pa završio.

563
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:07,940
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno, tu vam je ove stranke

564
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:09,480
[SPEAKER_02] AFD, desničarske,

565
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,260
[SPEAKER_02] koje su...

566
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:11,980
[SPEAKER_02] Ali i po cijeloj Evropskoj Uniji

567
00:34:11,980 --> 00:34:14,300
[SPEAKER_02] se vidi da je nezadovoljstvo veliko

568
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:16,559
[SPEAKER_02] i evo, čime je to rezultiralo,

569
00:34:16,559 --> 00:34:18,760
[SPEAKER_02] Schengen, imamo suspenziju Schengena

570
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] u gotovo cijeloj EU.

571
00:34:20,559 --> 00:34:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači li to da Hrvatsku

572
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] s ovim brojem

573
00:34:24,039 --> 00:34:25,679
[SPEAKER_01] useljenika

574
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] čekaju geta?

575
00:34:27,039 --> 00:34:29,239
[SPEAKER_02] Pa gledajte, znači,

576
00:34:29,239 --> 00:34:32,500
[SPEAKER_02] ova sva tema se svodi na to osnovno pitanje.

577
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:35,039
[SPEAKER_02] Kako da mi sada spriječimo getoizaciju?

578
00:34:35,039 --> 00:34:37,880
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, možemo sad puno o tome pričati,

579
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:38,980
[SPEAKER_02] ali sve se svodi samo na to pitanje.

580
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:39,699
[SPEAKER_02] Sami ste rekli,

581
00:34:39,699 --> 00:34:41,219
[SPEAKER_01] trećina ih ostaje.

582
00:34:41,219 --> 00:34:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] Oni se isto tako dolaze

583
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] nove njihove generacije, međusobno.

584
00:34:45,539 --> 00:34:47,159
[SPEAKER_02] Gledajte,

585
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:50,079
[SPEAKER_02] ono što moramo paziti je da ne treba

586
00:34:50,079 --> 00:34:53,039
[SPEAKER_02] stereotipe naglašavati.

587
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:56,460
[SPEAKER_02] vidite, imamo još jedan novi problem.

588
00:34:56,460 --> 00:34:56,840
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

589
00:34:56,840 --> 00:35:01,019
[SPEAKER_02] naš obrazomni sustav treba početi raditi na tome

590
00:35:01,019 --> 00:35:04,880
[SPEAKER_02] da priprema našu djecu za multikulturalno društvo,

591
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:08,239
[SPEAKER_02] jer mi uvozom strane radne snage

592
00:35:08,239 --> 00:35:11,380
[SPEAKER_02] uvozimo i multikulturalizam kao ideologiju.

593
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:14,179
[SPEAKER_02] sviđalo se to nekome ili ne?

594
00:35:14,179 --> 00:35:17,579
[SPEAKER_02] Radi ovakvih problema koji mogu nastati,

595
00:35:17,579 --> 00:35:19,800
[SPEAKER_02] mi moramo početi educirati našu djecu.

596
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:22,079
[SPEAKER_02] kao prvo u obrazovnom sustavu.

597
00:35:22,079 --> 00:35:22,539
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo,

598
00:35:22,539 --> 00:35:25,059
[SPEAKER_02] svatko ko uđe u Hrvatsku

599
00:35:25,059 --> 00:35:28,059
[SPEAKER_02] mora naprosto dobiti neku vrstu

600
00:35:28,059 --> 00:35:30,480
[SPEAKER_02] integracijskog priručnika i upute

601
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:32,340
[SPEAKER_02] što društvo očekuje od njega.

602
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:34,159
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ne možete vi osuditi,

603
00:35:34,159 --> 00:35:34,840
[SPEAKER_02] bio je primjer,

604
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:37,880
[SPEAKER_02] migrant je slikao djecu kako se igraju,

605
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,599
[SPEAKER_02] jel tako,

606
00:35:38,599 --> 00:35:40,119
[SPEAKER_02] negdje u pjesku,

607
00:35:40,119 --> 00:35:41,400
[SPEAKER_02] u nekakvom parku,

608
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:43,219
[SPEAKER_02] pa su roditelji napravili,

609
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:44,619
[SPEAKER_02] veliku frku,

610
00:35:44,619 --> 00:35:46,400
[SPEAKER_02] to je bilo nedavno u medijima,

611
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,800
[SPEAKER_02] ali čekajte,

612
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,960
[SPEAKER_02] pa da li taj čovjek zna

613
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:51,260
[SPEAKER_02] da se u Evropi ne smije slikati djecu?

614
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,559
[SPEAKER_02] Vjerojatno ne zna.

615
00:35:52,559 --> 00:35:53,519
[SPEAKER_02] E sad,

616
00:35:53,519 --> 00:35:56,480
[SPEAKER_02] vi kada mu date priručnik u kojem stoji,

617
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:58,019
[SPEAKER_02] što su prava,

618
00:35:58,019 --> 00:35:59,019
[SPEAKER_02] što su obveze,

619
00:35:59,019 --> 00:36:01,860
[SPEAKER_02] onda tek imate pravo od njega zahtijevati

620
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:03,019
[SPEAKER_02] da se drži toga.

621
00:36:03,019 --> 00:36:04,699
[SPEAKER_02] Jel smo li mi nešto tako napravili?

622
00:36:04,699 --> 00:36:06,119
[SPEAKER_02] Mi to nismo napravili,

623
00:36:06,119 --> 00:36:07,079
[SPEAKER_02] o tom vam i govorim.

624
00:36:07,079 --> 00:36:09,119
[SPEAKER_02] Mi sad imamo hitnu potrebu

625
00:36:09,119 --> 00:36:12,019
[SPEAKER_02] da započnemo procese integracije.

626
00:36:12,019 --> 00:36:13,159
[SPEAKER_02] Sve se svodi na to

627
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:15,239
[SPEAKER_02] i da spriječimo getoizaciju.

628
00:36:15,239 --> 00:36:17,460
[SPEAKER_02] Sad, pitali ste o getoizaciji.

629
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:17,940
[SPEAKER_02] Gledajte,

630
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:20,079
[SPEAKER_02] naš stambeni zakon

631
00:36:20,079 --> 00:36:21,780
[SPEAKER_02] koji sada je,

632
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:24,639
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, prošao prvo čitanje u Saboru,

633
00:36:24,639 --> 00:36:26,820
[SPEAKER_02] on predviđa,

634
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:29,780
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, sad je javnosti poznato

635
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:32,159
[SPEAKER_02] da 80% su vlasnika

636
00:36:32,159 --> 00:36:33,659
[SPEAKER_02] treba dati privolu,

637
00:36:33,659 --> 00:36:36,039
[SPEAKER_02] a ukoliko neko želi iznajmiti stan,

638
00:36:36,039 --> 00:36:37,099
[SPEAKER_02] to je definirano

639
00:36:37,099 --> 00:36:40,179
[SPEAKER_02] za više od četiri osobe

640
00:36:40,179 --> 00:36:41,940
[SPEAKER_02] koje nisu u srodstvu.

641
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:42,619
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro.

642
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] To znači,

643
00:36:43,559 --> 00:36:45,760
[SPEAKER_02] puno je sad tu implikacija

644
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:48,860
[SPEAKER_02] kojih zakonodavac nije bio sjestan.

645
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:50,000
[SPEAKER_02] Što će se dogoditi?

646
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,440
[SPEAKER_02] Skrivena namjera je očito bila

647
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:54,300
[SPEAKER_02] da se strane radnike

648
00:36:54,300 --> 00:36:55,199
[SPEAKER_02] iz zgrada,

649
00:36:55,199 --> 00:36:56,079
[SPEAKER_02] znači,

650
00:36:56,079 --> 00:36:58,760
[SPEAKER_02] dislocira.

651
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:02,360
[SPEAKER_02] Dogodilo se to zapravo

652
00:37:02,360 --> 00:37:03,639
[SPEAKER_02] da će vam predgrađa

653
00:37:03,639 --> 00:37:04,619
[SPEAKER_02] velikih gradova,

654
00:37:04,619 --> 00:37:05,920
[SPEAKER_02] prvenstveno Zagreba,

655
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:09,679
[SPEAKER_02] sada imati veliku zapravo

656
00:37:09,679 --> 00:37:15,119
[SPEAKER_02] mobilizaciju te radne snage,

657
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:17,719
[SPEAKER_02] koja će doći u, znači,

658
00:37:17,719 --> 00:37:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] kvartove na rubu,

659
00:37:19,559 --> 00:37:21,840
[SPEAKER_02] recimo Lučko, Leskovac, Dubrava,

660
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:22,599
[SPEAKER_02] tako dalje,

661
00:37:22,599 --> 00:37:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] jer tu ne morate tražiti

662
00:37:24,559 --> 00:37:26,000
[SPEAKER_02] dozvolu, nije od koga,

663
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,300
[SPEAKER_02] da stavite 20 ljudi u kuću,

664
00:37:28,300 --> 00:37:29,079
[SPEAKER_02] svoju.

665
00:37:30,079 --> 00:37:31,139
[SPEAKER_02] Po meni, znači,

666
00:37:31,139 --> 00:37:32,679
[SPEAKER_02] bi pravedno rješenje bilo

667
00:37:32,679 --> 00:37:34,079
[SPEAKER_02] da i susjedi, znači,

668
00:37:34,079 --> 00:37:36,139
[SPEAKER_02] u kućama imaju isto pravo

669
00:37:36,139 --> 00:37:37,460
[SPEAKER_02] kao i u stambenim zgradama.

670
00:37:37,460 --> 00:37:38,539
[SPEAKER_02] Odnosno, prvi susjedi.

671
00:37:38,539 --> 00:37:40,039
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je, prvi susjed

672
00:37:40,039 --> 00:37:41,480
[SPEAKER_02] da treba dati privolu,

673
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,519
[SPEAKER_02] jer zašto bi,

674
00:37:42,519 --> 00:37:44,400
[SPEAKER_02] zakon kaže sljedeće,

675
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:47,360
[SPEAKER_02] radi kvalitete života

676
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,840
[SPEAKER_02] u stambenim zgradama,

677
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,300
[SPEAKER_02] a zašto bi se onda narušila

678
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:52,239
[SPEAKER_02] kvaliteta života u predgrađima?

679
00:37:52,239 --> 00:37:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, zašto je onaj,

680
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] zašto bi trebao imati pravo

681
00:37:56,260 --> 00:37:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] na kvalitetni život,

682
00:37:57,219 --> 00:37:58,860
[SPEAKER_01] onaj u centru Zagreba, u zgradi?

683
00:37:58,860 --> 00:37:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo.

684
00:37:59,219 --> 00:38:00,800
[SPEAKER_01] Osim od nekog ko tamo,

685
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] eto u Botincu, možda ima kuću.

686
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo.

687
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:04,039
[SPEAKER_02] To je sad suština

688
00:38:04,039 --> 00:38:05,739
[SPEAKER_02] i da se još promijeniti,

689
00:38:05,739 --> 00:38:08,039
[SPEAKER_02] za mjesec dana će biti to

690
00:38:08,039 --> 00:38:09,300
[SPEAKER_02] završena priča.

691
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:09,960
[SPEAKER_02] I što mislite?

692
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:10,900
[SPEAKER_01] Kako će završiti?

693
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:13,880
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, Danska nam je pokazala kako,

694
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,440
[SPEAKER_02] Njemačka, Francuska,

695
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,460
[SPEAKER_02] pokazala nam je,

696
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:17,659
[SPEAKER_02] znači, Danska je sad

697
00:38:17,659 --> 00:38:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] u zadnjim vremenu

698
00:38:19,559 --> 00:38:21,300
[SPEAKER_02] donijela odredbe

699
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:22,719
[SPEAKER_02] koliko u određenom kvartu

700
00:38:22,719 --> 00:38:24,039
[SPEAKER_02] može biti useljenika.

701
00:38:24,039 --> 00:38:27,059
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, mi isto trebamo nešto slično,

702
00:38:27,059 --> 00:38:28,360
[SPEAKER_02] recimo 5%

703
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,360
[SPEAKER_02] po kvartu.

704
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:32,860
[SPEAKER_02] Recimo, ako vama počne,

705
