916
00:46:21,920 --> 00:46:25,940
[SPEAKER_02] Poljaci su uvezli Ukrajince upravo s tim.

917
00:46:25,940 --> 00:46:28,599
[SPEAKER_02] Ali Ukrajince nisu htjeli doći k nama baš previše.

918
00:46:28,599 --> 00:46:30,860
[SPEAKER_02] Upravo, ne ovo govorim prije rata.

919
00:46:30,860 --> 00:46:32,500
