920
00:46:32,500 --> 00:46:34,519
[SPEAKER_02] Želimo kulturološki bliži narod.

921
00:46:34,519 --> 00:46:36,400
[SPEAKER_02] Kod nas, znači, se dogodilo

922
00:46:36,400 --> 00:46:39,900
[SPEAKER_02] da mi propuštamo, recimo, Hrvate iz BiH

923
00:46:39,900 --> 00:46:42,559
[SPEAKER_02] do medicinska sestra

924
00:46:42,559 --> 00:46:43,880
