927
00:46:48,840 --> 00:46:50,099
[SPEAKER_02] da ih zadržimo ovdje.

928
00:46:50,099 --> 00:46:52,639
[SPEAKER_02] Onda smo dvostruko napravili

929
00:46:52,639 --> 00:46:55,880
[SPEAKER_02] dobro rješenje.

930
00:46:55,880 --> 00:46:57,619
[SPEAKER_02] Zadržali smo Hrvate na ovim

931
00:46:57,619 --> 00:46:59,159
[SPEAKER_02] svojim etničkim prostorima.

932
00:46:59,239 --> 00:47:01,659
[SPEAKER_02] Nije vam isto kad neko ode u Dublin

933
00:47:01,659 --> 00:47:04,159
[SPEAKER_02] i kad je u Osijeku, recimo,

934
00:47:04,159 --> 00:47:05,920
[SPEAKER_02] a iz Bosanske posavine.

935
00:47:05,920 --> 00:47:08,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, na taj način zadržavamo

936
00:47:08,480 --> 00:47:11,300
[SPEAKER_02] i konstitutivnost i opstojnost Hrvata u BiH.

937
00:47:11,300 --> 00:47:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] To je i političko bitno pitanje.

938
00:47:13,559 --> 00:47:15,739
[SPEAKER_02] Jel tamo Hrvati, naprosto,

939
00:47:15,739 --> 00:47:18,800
[SPEAKER_02] do 2050. će biti nacionalna manjina.

940
00:47:18,800 --> 00:47:22,159
[SPEAKER_02] Uopće, više neće biti konstitutiva narod.

941
00:47:22,159 --> 00:47:24,219
[SPEAKER_02] Jel će vas većinski narod pita,

942
00:47:24,219 --> 00:47:26,719
[SPEAKER_02] pa kako ti možeš imati isto pravo

943
00:47:26,719 --> 00:47:29,380
[SPEAKER_02] kao ja, vas je ukupno 50 tisuća,

944
