[SPEAKER_02] nas je 3 milijuna.

945
00:47:30,880 --> 00:47:34,199
[SPEAKER_02] To su omjeri, znači,

946
00:47:34,199 --> 00:47:36,420
[SPEAKER_02] što se tiče muslimanskog stanovništva

947
00:47:36,420 --> 00:47:39,880
[SPEAKER_02] i hrvatskog sredinom ovog stoljeća,

948
00:47:39,880 --> 00:47:41,280
[SPEAKER_02] jel i u Bosni i Hercegovini.

949
00:47:41,280 --> 00:47:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] U Hrvatskoj, inače,

950
00:47:42,860 --> 00:47:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] proteklih pet godina,

951
00:47:44,320 --> 00:47:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] našla sam podatak,

952
00:47:45,159 --> 00:47:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] uselilo više stranih ratnika

953
00:47:46,880 --> 00:47:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] iz trećih zemalja,

954
00:47:47,920 --> 00:47:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] nego što ukupno ima Hrvata

955
00:47:49,260 --> 00:47:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] u Kanadi, Australiji ili Čileu.

956
00:47:51,039 --> 00:47:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ti se nikad neće vratiti.

957
00:47:52,679 --> 00:47:54,880
[SPEAKER_02] To je sad u ovoj mojoj novoj knjizi

958
00:47:54,880 --> 00:47:57,019
[SPEAKER_02] suvremene migracije i opštene nacije.

959
00:47:57,019 --> 00:47:58,780
[SPEAKER_02] Samo vas citiram, samo vas danas citiram.

960
00:47:58,920 --> 00:48:01,539
[SPEAKER_02] To je, izići će kod školske knjige,

961
00:48:01,539 --> 00:48:02,980
[SPEAKER_02] na Interliberu će biti,

962
00:48:02,980 --> 00:48:05,159
[SPEAKER_02] ako smijem reklamirati,

963
00:48:05,159 --> 00:48:07,519
[SPEAKER_02] će biti promocija knjige.

964
00:48:07,519 --> 00:48:12,219
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, naša ideja je

965
00:48:12,219 --> 00:48:13,739
[SPEAKER_02] dijaspora će nas spasiti.

966
00:48:13,739 --> 00:48:15,599
[SPEAKER_02] I ja sam prvi koji bi volio

967
00:48:15,599 --> 00:48:16,539
[SPEAKER_02] da se to dogodi.

968
00:48:16,539 --> 00:48:19,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ali isto treba uzeti u opet

969
00:48:19,460 --> 00:48:21,099
[SPEAKER_02] referentne točke i okvir.

970
00:48:21,099 --> 00:48:23,940
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, naša dijaspora je danas manja

971
