[SPEAKER_02] od svake godine broja stranih radnika

972
00:48:26,260 --> 00:48:27,539
[SPEAKER_02] koji ulazi u zemlju.

973
00:48:28,920 --> 00:48:30,380
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da to je isto...

974
00:48:30,380 --> 00:48:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, taj kodač se okreće

975
00:48:32,300 --> 00:48:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] i tu nema više sada stajanja.

976
00:48:33,380 --> 00:48:35,739
[SPEAKER_02] Gajte, nama dođe 180 tisća...

977
00:48:35,739 --> 00:48:36,300
[SPEAKER_02] Stranaca?

978
00:48:36,300 --> 00:48:38,619
[SPEAKER_02] Ali tu moramo biti pošteni

979
00:48:38,619 --> 00:48:41,159
[SPEAKER_02] i reći da ne dižemo moralnu paniku.

980
00:48:41,159 --> 00:48:43,300
[SPEAKER_02] 50% je to ipak

981
