[SPEAKER_02] iz jugoistoka Evrope.

982
00:48:45,079 --> 00:48:47,019
[SPEAKER_02] Nije to sve Afrika i Azija.

983
00:48:47,019 --> 00:48:49,219
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo što treba

984
