[SPEAKER_02] naglasiti, znači,

985
00:48:50,800 --> 00:48:53,699
[SPEAKER_02] ilegalne migracije su jedana prema deset.

986
00:48:54,099 --> 00:48:55,639
[SPEAKER_02] Deset puta više dolazi

987
00:48:55,639 --> 00:48:56,980
[SPEAKER_02] ilegalnim migracijama.

988
00:48:56,980 --> 00:48:59,480
[SPEAKER_02] I u Hrvatsku i na razine Evropske unije.

989
00:48:59,480 --> 00:49:03,480
[SPEAKER_02] Istina je,

990
00:49:03,480 --> 00:49:05,980
[SPEAKER_02] prošle godine smo imali enormno puno

991
00:49:05,980 --> 00:49:07,820
[SPEAKER_02] ilegalne migracije,

992
00:49:07,820 --> 00:49:09,780
[SPEAKER_02] to je 65 tisuća čak.

993
00:49:09,780 --> 00:49:13,480
[SPEAKER_02] U pravilu je ona, znači,

994
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:14,420
[SPEAKER_02] znatno niža,

995
00:49:14,420 --> 00:49:15,820
[SPEAKER_02] ali da se razumijemo,

996
00:49:15,820 --> 00:49:17,559
[SPEAKER_02] zato se i zove ilegalna,

997
00:49:17,559 --> 00:49:19,179
[SPEAKER_02] jer niko ne zna koliko je.

998
00:49:19,179 --> 00:49:21,960
[SPEAKER_02] Zapravo, pravu brojku ne zna nitko.

999
00:49:22,559 --> 00:49:24,380
[SPEAKER_02] To vam je ovo što je, znači,

1000
00:49:24,380 --> 00:49:26,840
