1001
00:49:26,840 --> 00:49:28,739
[SPEAKER_02] pa su oni zatražili azijel.

1002
00:49:28,739 --> 00:49:30,940
[SPEAKER_02] To je već tematizirano,

1003
00:49:30,940 --> 00:49:32,619
[SPEAKER_02] absurd te situacije.

1004
00:49:32,619 --> 00:49:33,880
[SPEAKER_01] To pratim već godinama.

1005
00:49:33,880 --> 00:49:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, gospodine Juriću,

1006
00:49:35,420 --> 00:49:36,980
[SPEAKER_01] sad kad ste ih već spomenuli,

1007
00:49:36,980 --> 00:49:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] te ilegalne migracije,

1008
00:49:38,500 --> 00:49:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] u cijeloj toj priči

1009
00:49:40,920 --> 00:49:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] oko ilegalnih migracija,

1010
00:49:42,239 --> 00:49:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] danas kad čitamo bilo koje,

1011
00:49:44,199 --> 00:49:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] izvještaje bilo koje policijske uprave

1012
00:49:46,619 --> 00:49:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] koja uhvati švercere migranata

1013
00:49:48,659 --> 00:49:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] i s njima ilegalne migrante,

1014
00:49:50,320 --> 00:49:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] obavezno je, svi ilegalni migranti

1015
00:49:52,780 --> 00:49:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] zatražili su azil.

1016
00:49:54,380 --> 00:49:58,820
[SPEAKER_02] Pa gledajte, to vam je tematizirano.

1017
00:49:58,820 --> 00:50:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] Što to donosi nama u budućnosti.

1018
00:50:00,820 --> 00:50:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane, nekako se bilo onako

1019
00:50:02,820 --> 00:50:04,980
[SPEAKER_01] stidljivo spomenula ona priča

1020
00:50:04,980 --> 00:50:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] o vraćanjima određenih broja ljudi,

1021
00:50:07,400 --> 00:50:08,199
[SPEAKER_01] onim kvotama,

1022
00:50:08,199 --> 00:50:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] nekim tajnim avionima natragu u Hrvatsku.

1023
00:50:10,860 --> 00:50:12,059
[SPEAKER_01] Nitko o tome ne priča.

1024
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, postoji li mogućnost da ti koji su

1025
00:50:15,420 --> 00:50:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] zatražili u Hrvatskoj azil sutra odu,

1026
00:50:17,400 --> 00:50:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] a otić će, pa budu nekim odlukama

1027
00:50:19,920 --> 00:50:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] nekih drugih zemalja vraćeni u zemlju

1028
00:50:21,940 --> 00:50:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj su prvotno

1029
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] zatražili azil?

1030
00:50:25,139 --> 00:50:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1031
00:50:25,599 --> 00:50:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] Što ćemo postati hot spot?

1032
00:50:26,960 --> 00:50:29,099
[SPEAKER_02] Gledajte, znači, opet tu,

1033
00:50:29,099 --> 00:50:32,159
[SPEAKER_02] ono što je maglovito u javnosti

1034
00:50:32,159 --> 00:50:33,820
[SPEAKER_02] je što se sve migracije stavljaju

1035
00:50:33,820 --> 00:50:34,420
[SPEAKER_02] u isti koš.

1036
00:50:34,420 --> 00:50:35,579
[SPEAKER_02] Pa se onda kaže,

1037
00:50:35,579 --> 00:50:38,019
[SPEAKER_02] migrant je i izbjeglica iz Ukrajine,

1038
00:50:38,019 --> 00:50:39,880
[SPEAKER_02] i ilegalni migrant,

1039
00:50:39,880 --> 00:50:41,019
[SPEAKER_02] i azilant,

1040
00:50:41,019 --> 00:50:42,360
[SPEAKER_02] i radni migrant,

1041
