[SPEAKER_02] i povratnik Hrvati z Kanade.

1042
00:50:44,679 --> 00:50:45,639
[SPEAKER_02] A po me nije.

1043
00:50:45,639 --> 00:50:47,340
[SPEAKER_02] To su pet rašitih kategorija,

1044
00:50:47,340 --> 00:50:49,300
[SPEAKER_02] plus šesta kategorija su bogati

1045
00:50:49,300 --> 00:50:50,659
[SPEAKER_02] njemački umirovljenici

1046
00:50:50,659 --> 00:50:52,840
[SPEAKER_02] koji kupuju Hrvatsku obalu.

1047
00:50:52,840 --> 00:50:54,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ne samo oni, i slovenski,

1048
00:50:54,679 --> 00:50:55,460
[SPEAKER_02] i italijanski,

1049
00:50:55,460 --> 00:50:57,079
[SPEAKER_02] to vam je još jedan poseban,

1050
00:50:57,079 --> 00:50:58,840
[SPEAKER_02] znači posebna tema,

1051
00:50:58,840 --> 00:51:00,920
[SPEAKER_02] ako stigne o možemo od tome,

1052
00:51:00,920 --> 00:51:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] sad, znači ilegalne migracije.

1053
00:51:02,840 --> 00:51:06,260
[SPEAKER_02] Potpuno je jasno da tu treba imati stav

1054
00:51:06,260 --> 00:51:08,480
[SPEAKER_02] da se azil može tražiti

1055
00:51:08,480 --> 00:51:11,119
[SPEAKER_02] samo prije ulaska na teritoriju

1056
00:51:11,119 --> 00:51:12,059
[SPEAKER_02] Evropske unije.

1057
00:51:12,059 --> 00:51:13,659
[SPEAKER_02] Točno je neke zemlje,

1058
00:51:13,659 --> 00:51:14,619
[SPEAKER_02] recimo ako je rat,

1059
00:51:14,619 --> 00:51:16,980
[SPEAKER_02] ne možeš naravno tamo u veleposlanstvu,

1060
00:51:16,980 --> 00:51:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] ali možeš u prvoj zemlji,

1061
00:51:18,420 --> 00:51:20,239
[SPEAKER_02] koja ti je na putu, da.

1062
00:51:20,239 --> 00:51:23,900
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo, znači ako je netko naprosto rekao

1063
00:51:23,900 --> 00:51:24,840
[SPEAKER_02] azil, azil,

1064
00:51:24,840 --> 00:51:27,699
[SPEAKER_02] i na jedan put u tom društvu

1065
00:51:27,699 --> 00:51:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] treba dobiti pravo na rad,

1066
00:51:29,559 --> 00:51:31,619
[SPEAKER_02] besplatan smješta i tako dalje,

1067
00:51:31,820 --> 00:51:33,039
[SPEAKER_02] a naša, recimo,

1068
00:51:33,039 --> 00:51:36,079
[SPEAKER_02] naši roditelji imaju mirovinu,

1069
00:51:36,079 --> 00:51:37,239
[SPEAKER_02] znatno manju

1070
00:51:37,239 --> 00:51:40,159
[SPEAKER_02] od pomoći koja će se davati

1071
00:51:40,159 --> 00:51:41,460
[SPEAKER_02] za ilegalne migrante,

1072
00:51:41,460 --> 00:51:43,920
[SPEAKER_02] naravno da je to

1073
00:51:43,920 --> 00:51:45,380
[SPEAKER_02] iz socijalnog, znači,

1074
00:51:45,380 --> 00:51:46,380
[SPEAKER_02] kuta,

1075
00:51:46,380 --> 00:51:47,539
[SPEAKER_02] nepravedno.

1076
00:51:49,119 --> 00:51:50,179
[SPEAKER_02] ilegalna imigracija,

1077
00:51:50,179 --> 00:51:51,380
[SPEAKER_02] ovam najbolji primjer,

1078
00:51:51,380 --> 00:51:52,659
[SPEAKER_02] moj student,

1079
00:51:52,659 --> 00:51:53,840
[SPEAKER_02] XY,

1080
00:51:53,840 --> 00:51:56,199
[SPEAKER_02] stvarna situacija,

1081
00:51:56,199 --> 00:51:56,719
[SPEAKER_02] mi kaže,

1082
00:51:56,719 --> 00:51:57,400
[SPEAKER_02] profesore,

1083
00:51:57,400 --> 00:52:00,599
[SPEAKER_02] ja radim sa XY iz Afrike,

1084
00:52:00,599 --> 00:52:02,159
[SPEAKER_02] on je ilegalni imigrant,

1085
00:52:02,739 --> 00:52:05,119
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, njemu je plaćen hotel,

1086
00:52:05,119 --> 00:52:05,940
[SPEAKER_02] porin,

1087
00:52:05,940 --> 00:52:09,059
[SPEAKER_02] on ima istu visinu plaće kao ja,

1088
00:52:09,059 --> 00:52:11,860
[SPEAKER_02] a ja imam ženu i djete koja ne radi,

1089
00:52:11,860 --> 00:52:15,039
[SPEAKER_02] imamo istu plaću,

1090
00:52:15,340 --> 00:52:15,699
[SPEAKER_02] sad,

1091
00:52:15,699 --> 00:52:18,739
[SPEAKER_02] on naravno će nazvat sutra svog rođaka

1092
00:52:18,739 --> 00:52:19,159
[SPEAKER_02] i reći,

1093
00:52:19,159 --> 00:52:21,300
[SPEAKER_02] gledajte, ovdje ima zemlja koja daje sve,

1094
00:52:21,300 --> 00:52:22,460
[SPEAKER_02] možeš raditi,

1095
00:52:22,460 --> 00:52:24,800
