1096
00:52:24,800 --> 00:52:25,940
[SPEAKER_02] azilantima da radi.

1097
00:52:25,940 --> 00:52:27,219
[SPEAKER_02] Što smo napravili?

1098
00:52:27,219 --> 00:52:29,159
